  "title": "feat(range): support new routing system",
  "body": "This updates `range` lifecycle methods to support the new routing system.\r\n\r\n## `getWidgetState` changes\r\n\r\nThis method ignores previous UI state values. Otherwise, new values gets skipped.\r\n\r\n## `getWidgetSearchParameters` changes\r\n\r\nThis method is self-contained. It sets both `disjunctiveFacets` and `numericRefinements`. It doesn't overwrite other `numericRefinements` but only sets the one coming from `widgetParams.attribute` to an empty object.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n_`getConfiguration` will be removed later to not break everything._",
